 {
  "date": "Thu, 16 Jan 2014 07:00:00 EST", 
  "link": "http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/16/steam-controller-changes/", 
  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/gaming/\" rel=\"tag\">游戏产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/16/steam-controller-changes/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/548eb1e1d865a554fc0525915aab7ae6/steamcontroller_slide_630pxhedimg.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\nBeta 测试看来有了效果，今天早些时候 Valve 宣布，在今年晚些时候推出市场时，将会把 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/steamcontroller\">Steam Controller</a> 现有的触控屏幕换成实体按键。具体会采用什么样的设计现在还不知道，但有消息称应该会是 D-pad 加标准 A/B/X/Y 四键的布局。<br />\n<br />\n另外，根据 <a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/tag/steamdevdays\">Steam Dev Days</a> 大会参与者的推文来看，Valve 还会推出全新的「鬼影（ghosting）」模式（我们猜测可能是把按键布局做成影像加到屏幕上去）。而且他们还会为游戏开发者准备用于集成 Steam Controller 的 API，最多可支持 16 人同时游戏。<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/valve-controller-prototypes/\">Valve Controller Prototypes</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/valve-controller-prototypes/6454503/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc07963-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/valve-controller-prototypes/6454504/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc07983-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/valve-controller-prototypes/6454505/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc07986-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/valve-controller-prototypes/6454506/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc07989-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/valve-controller-prototypes/6454507/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc07990-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/01/15/steam-controller-changes/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23steamdevdays&amp;src=hash\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/16/steam-controller-changes/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20809201/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/16/steam-controller-changes/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
